      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cape_Vincent%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "In 1880 the Thousand Islands were publicized, turning Cape Vincent into a summer retreat for wealthy vacationers seeking bass fishing and a mild climate.",
